scene.message:
Mark: Owowowow!{nl}
That smarts~{waitkey}{clearbox}Hm?{wait_fr:88} I see...{nl}
so this compact{nl}
carried us here...{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Looks like it worked...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
This is the forest where the{nl}
child Sonomura was, I think.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Bingo!!{nl}
This is Child Maki's{nl}
forest!{waitkey}

Brown: Hey, we did it!!{nl}
This is little Maki's{nl}
forest, isn't it?!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Super lucky!!{nl}
This is chibi Sonomura's{nl}
forest, right?!

Maki's Mother: Why have you{nl}
come back?! What happened{nl}
with Kandori?!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: I'm not sure...{nl}
After I sent you all off,{nl}
I thought I heard Maki again{waitkey}{clearbox}and next I knew,{nl}
I was here... But why{nl}
have you come back?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: ......{wait_fr:88}{nl}
It can't be... such a thing...{waitkey}Then what about Maki?!{nl}
What will become of Maki?!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Left alone, at best{nl}
she stays that way for life,{nl}
at worst...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: No...{nl}
Can nothing be done?!{nl}
This is too cruel!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Ma'am, calm down!!{nl}
That's exactly why{nl}
we came back.

Brown: It'll be fine,{nl}
just trust us! Climb aboard{nl}
like it's a sinking mud boat!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Right, right, a great{nl}
ship! Totally a-okay!!{nl}
Bwahahaha!!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hey Nanjo... this is{nl}
his real self. So much{nl}
for "self-improvement"...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Indeed... this degree{nl}
of foolishness is a{nl}
natural gift.{waitkey}{clearbox}He hardly looks like a man{nl}
who'd faint over something{nl}
so crude as soiling himself.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Don't worry, Sonomura{nl}
Mama! Ayase may not look it,{nl}
but Ayase's reliable!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: That was{nl}
Maki's voice?! She's{nl}
deeper inside!{waitkey}

Mark: Let's go!!{nl}
Little Sonomura might{nl}
know something!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: Wait!{nl}
Take me with you!{nl}
I'm Maki's mother!{waitkey}I can't just leave my own{nl}
daughter to suffer!

Nanjo: ...{wait_fr:88}Very well.{nl}
But this forest is dangerous.{nl}
I can't guarantee your life.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Heh... she's a good{nl}
mom, huh. Pretty, too.{waitkey}{clearbox}My old lady...{wait_fr:88} she's{nl}
just a nag, but she's{nl}
alive and kicking, I bet!{waitkey}

Nanjo: A woman like her is{nl}
a true mother... I don't{nl}
even know my mom's birthday.{clearbox}Even at home, all but{nl}
Yamaoka were strangers.{nl}
All I got was money, things.{clearbox}{ctl0f:1}, we WILL reunite{nl}
her with Sonomura - even{nl}
at the cost of our lives.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Still, this whole{nl}
affair gives me much{nl}
to think about.{waitkey}{clearbox}The existence of multiple{nl}
selves... I never once{nl}
considered it, but even I{waitkey}must acknowledge it now.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
That's just how moms are...{nl}
Kids just don't notice it.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: How long you planning{nl}
to stay here? Aren't we{nl}
going to the shrine?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Oh, good!{nl}
I was worried you might{nl}
find it odd!{waitkey}{ctl07:1}... Thanks...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: The shrine's next,{nl}
right? "Haste makes waste"!{waitkey}What? That's "not what it{nl}
means"? Whatever - it's{nl}
Brown-speak!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hmm~{nl}
{ctl0f:1}, when you look{nl}
closely, you're a catch!{waitkey}{clearbox}Want Ayase to register you{nl}
as a husband candidate?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Beep! Registered!{nl}
From now on, you'll work{nl}
like a horse for Ayase!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: What?!{nl}
Ayase's not good enough?!{nl}
Fine! See if Ayase cares!!{waitkey}I'll work you even harder!!{waitkey}{ret}Ayase: We're going to the{nl}
shrine, right? With all this{nl}
walking, maybe it counts{waitkey}as a little diet?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: I'm... a{nl}
useless mother. Whenever{nl}
she suffers, I can never{waitkey}do a thing for her...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: The real me is next...{nl}
Just how many of me{nl}
are there, anyway?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Child Maki...{nl}
all alone in such a{nl}
lonely place...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Child Maki...{nl}
all alone in such a{nl}
lonely place...{waitkey}{ret}
